1782027162385549	paintop-dev	itc:v3:AWKTkkmcyckyeZEAAAAAQa6q3a6te0AAAAEz3QU		item.comment	bn-97e	{"body":"M2 exit gate bn-1r2 DONE and green (commit 32e83b0 in workspace m2-build): ci/m2-gate.sh + 'just m2-gate' assert all four M2 criteria — (1) tiled==whole bit-identical, (2) ROI==full differential, (3) 4K masked edit touches only the predicted halo-expanded tiles (new crates/paintop-cpu/tests/masked_edit_4k.rs; executed-tile count <= conservative dilation prediction; emits tiles.json artifact), (4) cache replay zero-recompute — plus an M1 no-regression re-run. just check / test / verify-ops (44 ops) all green. NOT closing this umbrella: children bn-3mm (open), bn-3r8 (doing), bn-6kl (doing) are still owned by paintop-dev and not yet done. Lead should close bn-97e once those land."}	blake3:BFuHvw7hwggKGs4n0wIpzwoeXoYJd20Fh0l_NrJC3qw
