1782053799852626	paintop-dev	itc:v3:AWKTkkmcyckyeZEAAAAAQa6q3a6te0AAAAEzvAc		item.update	bn-3jk	{"field":"description","value":"**What:** Close M4 (plan.md §19 M4 exit criteria) via a CI gate (`ci/m4-gate.sh` + `just m4-gate`): (1) solver-style ops (Poisson, screened-Poisson, reaction-diffusion, PatchMatch, local optimizer) expose convergence/progress metrics in their reports; (2) iterative or seeded ops have deterministic seed/ordering rules with rerun assertions; (3) required M4 ops have synthetic fixtures with known or bounded outcomes through verify-op; (4) performance + memory scale are characterized and uploaded as artifacts; (5) orientation/frequency analysis ops cover their covariance/preservation contracts. NOTE: EDT + SDF mask algebra already shipped in M1.5 (`bn-9oi`), and the FFT complex-spectrum stretch bone (`bn-2bg`) is optional/punt and intentionally outside this required gate.\n**Acceptance:** all required M4 criteria pass in CI across required M4 ops; M1/M1.5/M2/M3 gates still green; perf/memory artifacts uploaded.\n**Exit gate:** CI \"M4 classical magic\" job green; `just m4-gate` 0; `just check` 0.\n**Refs:** plan.md §1428-§1446 (M4); M1.5 `bn-9oi` (EDT/SDF already done); optional stretch `bn-2bg` excluded from this gate. **Depends on:** required M4 goals/tasks only."}	blake3:ryp6SzRXgIPc4XDj6msLTbE82QaUz8OUEU3PRcpytNk
